        },
        {
            "id": 30,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   你在龍門待的有點久了，卡彭。也許你該回憶一下怎麼和我說話，我才是首領。",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 31,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028#3",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 32,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   坐下，你這蠢貨，敘拉古的生意越來越差就是因為你的好脾氣。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 33,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028#3",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 34,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   你在龍門待了七八年，除了學到幾句龍門粗口，你又幹了什麼？眼睜睜看著我們的管道越來越少？",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 35,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028#3",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 36,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   至少昨天贏得了那位支持的人是我，而你，差點毀了我這麼長久的努力。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 37,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   還有，在龍門我們平起平坐，“首領”。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 38,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 39,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   鼠王在龍門搞的這一套，不都是敘拉古玩爛了的把戲？",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 40,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 41,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   但是你把敘拉古的一手好牌打得稀爛。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 42,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 43,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   而你就是我手裡最爛的一張牌。",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 44,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 45,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   我們會在龍門佔據一席之地的。好好想想，一座疲憊不堪、暗流湧動的城市，這裡會成為家族的下一個故土。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 46,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 47,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   只有敘拉古的土地會尊重我們，卡彭，別忘了被趕出那張桌子，夾著尾巴離開敘拉古的恥辱。",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 48,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 49,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   信條餵不飽任何人。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 50,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 51,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   哼。",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 52,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 53,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   魏彥吾在這座城市定下了規則，只要不過界，我們依舊可以在這裡大展拳腳，龍門需要一些“人情產業”。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 54,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 55,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   ......有幾年沒見，你越來越讓我感到厭倦了。",
                "name": "甘比諾"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 56,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 57,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "   彼此彼此，首領。",
                "name": "卡彭"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 58,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_028#3",
                "name2": "avg_npc_027#2",
                "focus": 1.0
